On the ``world knowledge'' direction, 
early works, using BERT, elicit knowledge about movie, music and book genres [DBLP:conf/recsys/PenhaH20]. Recent works prompt large language models (LLMs), such as GPT or Llama, to generate item rankings for user-specific recommendations [hou2023large,wang2023zero] or predict user ratings [kang2023llms], in a zero-shot 
or few-shot 
fashion. 
{Our experiments include [hou2023large] as an LLM-powered baseline.}